      "text": "Mussa na familia yake wanaishi katika kijiji kidogo nchini Uganda.\nHupanda mahindi kwenye shamba lao dogo mara mbili kila mwaka."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/venmaitran%40hotmail.com%2fcbbe3c1c-1a50-4206-9c8c-72b5880d42fb%2fMoses+and+the+Very+Good+Farm%2fAOR_OFDB029.png",
      "text": "Kadri miaka ilivyopita, familia ya Mussa iliendelea kulima kwenye ardhi na udongo ukachoka.\nMahindi hayakustawi vizuri.\nFamilia ya Mussa ikawa na hasira sana (ikagadhibika)"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/venmaitran%40hotmail.com%2fcbbe3c1c-1a50-4206-9c8c-72b5880d42fb%2fMoses+and+the+Very+Good+Farm%2fAOR_4O.png",
      "text": "Mussa akatembelea shamba la mtu kijiji kingine.\nMussa akajifunza mengi kuhusu njia za kilimo bora toka kwa mtu na shamba lake."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/venmaitran%40hotmail.com%2fcbbe3c1c-1a50-4206-9c8c-72b5880d42fb%2fMoses+and+the+Very+Good+Farm%2fAOR_th00114b.png",
      "text": "Mussa kajifunza kuandaa mbolea kwa kutumia majani yaliyo katwa mboji na maganda toka kwenye vyakula, matunda na mbogamboga. Mbolea ikarutubisha udongo."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
